cu.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause ASN.1 encoding/decoding configuration failure and protocol message issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FDM to an out-of-range value (100) will cause invalid PRACH FDM configuration and RACH procedure failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FDM 設定為超出範圍的值 (100)，會導致無效的 PRACH FDM 配置，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
